Event Manager
Responsibilities
The job responsibility includes but not limited the following:Build a concept for a specified target market in a lounge environmentMaintain the consistency of the entertainment and service of the loungeInnovatively program entertainment and events in a periodical basisDraw and socialize in a community which suits to the concept of the loungePay attention to details for all marketing materials and operationsCoordinate with lounge manager for a better lounge experienceMarket aggressively the products, entertainment and service of the loungeAttend marketing and community events to expose the brand of the lounge Requirements: Age not more 40 years oldBachelor degree in hospitality or tourism industryHave a minimum of 5 year experience in hospitality industryHave extensive links to community and entertainment providerPossess sensitive taste to suit the market demand in lounge businessGood command in EnglishAbility to work under pressureHave a strong influence and a sense of belongingKnowledgeable in lounge operation and SOPsGood communication skills & team work Please address your application letter along with your resume and a recent photograph to:hrd@therych.comThe Sultan Hotel Lobby Lagoon Tower Jl. Jenderal Gatot Subroto,Kel. Gelora, Kec. Tanah Abang, Jakarta Pusat (Kode Pos 10002)Contact person 021-5707122 ext. 121
